				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: Chinese Economic Nationalism
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1849730">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							<div class="bbcode_container">
	<div class="bbcode_quote">
		<div class="quote_container">
			<div class="bbcode_quote_container"></div>
			
				<div class="bbcode_postedby">
					<img src="images/misc/quote_icon.png" alt="Quote" /> Originally Posted by <strong>PPatty</strong>
					<a href="showthread.php?s=2f1c020babc86faf2681e53c14599bb3&amp;p=1849726#post1849726" rel="nofollow"><img class="inlineimg" src="images/buttons/viewpost-right.png" alt="View Post" /></a>
				</div>
				<div class="message">Why won't they just be our friends? Or why we won't we be theirs?</div>
			
		</div>
	</div>
</div>When Putin invaded Ukraine, it was kind of hard to do the whole &quot;let's be friends and sing kumbaya&quot; thing.<br />
<br />
With China, there is a whole ethnic nationalism which largely centers around enlarging its territory and conquering various places, and getting the best of the United States.  It's kind of hard to 'just be friends' with a country when they are aggressively stealing your technology and pressing territorial claims into rival territories. OK they can have Tibet if they want and destroy Tibetan culture, but now there's more and more territories to expand. They also have this nasty policy where they steal technology, push American firms out of the market, and have discriminatory policies which say that only Chinese can hold management positions at certain levels. The reality is that they are two pretty nasty authoritarian regimes that do nasty authoritarian stuff, and worse want to do all sorts of nasty authoritarian stuff just to legitimize their regimes. <br />
<br />
Over here we are writing about &quot;the US and China should play fair&quot;; over there people are talking about &quot;China's new policy will PK the United States&quot; and the news will have similar reportage that does not use the word &quot;PK&quot; ( a loan word from English). The short of the story is that China wants to PK the US, and if you've played on a PK server you know how hard it is to be friends with someone who wants to PK you.  To drive the point home, here is an image of a book or something someone made titled &quot;China PKs America&quot;:<br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.graffe.com/forums/attachment.php?s=2f1c020babc86faf2681e53c14599bb3&amp;attachmentid=4559&amp;d=1457915621"  title="Name:  1413252961-1581613733.jpg
Views: 41
Size:  79.2 KB">1413252961-1581613733.jpg</a><br />
<br />
<br />
If that wasn't enough, here is a Phoenix TV television program cutely titled &quot;How long until China PKs the United States Aircraft Carrier&quot;<br />
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VCpGcLyLFZI" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VCpGcLyLFZI</a><br />
<br />
These fuckers want to PK us!!!! Literally PK!!!<br />
<br />
Honestly we should be out fucking all of the Chinese women until there are no more women for the Chinese to fuck, and then some Chinese man professor does academic research on why white women don't want to fuck Chinese men.  Oh roflcopter it already happened:<br />
<a href="http://www.speakingofchina.com/ask-the-yangxifu/what-western-women-think-of-chinese-men/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://www.speakingofchina.com/ask-t...f-chinese-men/</a><br />
<br />
Gentlemen, if we just fuck ALL of the good looking women in China, the country will literally collapse in on itself because<br />
<br />
CHINESE MEN ONLY WANT TO MARRY VIRGINS!!! (for the most part)<br />
<br />
<br />
So the strategy is: fuck all the hot girls in the country, document everything. Get the hell out of dodge and then reveal all. Some dude actually did this, he banged like 200 Chinese women and then told all. (David Marriott) He's actually considered a serious threat to Chinese national security because of his Wei Wang.  But you are asking me: Istari, how will I ever fuck hundreds of Chines women? Sir, I will tell you! Go to China and teach English for a year. Peace corps or whatever. Chinese women will literally prostitute themselves out for a chance to practice English. I have never done this myself, but I have been offered it many times. Also if you buy the girl dinner there is some weird cultural conditioning that makes them want to jump into bed. Where to find all these girls? Language exchange boards! Literally thousands of women on the internet prostitute themselves out for English practice this way. (I have a whole different racket going on - see my other post)<br />
<br />
After you get about 200 and DOCUMENT EVERYTHING (names!!! Chinese spellings too!) DROP THE BOMB GENTLEMEN AND GET THE HELL OUT OF DODGE!!!!<br />
<br />
I estimate that if we could send just 30,000 English speaking convicts to China (who needs college graduates?) they would neutralize the marriage prospects of about 6,000,000 Chinese couples per year - the country would simply implode in on itself and some sort of democratic revolution would take place.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
